txt.en: 'I've roved all over the Shire, and there are lots of places to kick up your heels, but Waymeet's the best!'
'My fellows here are bringing goods from the Blue Mountains, by way of Needlehole.'
'Yes, sir, the people of Waymeet know how to relax!'
'I'd best be careful...my sister's always keeping tabs on me when I come through Waymeet, so I don't get into trouble.'
